The  carnival is about to happen in a few weeks and I'm helping organizing the one in <a href="http://pampus-lollebroek.nl/">our neighbourhood</a>. It's quite a big parade with at least 95 (and counting) groups participating.

About 60.000 people are watching this on the route of aprox. 8km and it's quite chaotic at some places. To be of a better service to the spectators I've created an website and iPhone app to track the head of this parade so people can view it's current position.

The iPhone app uploads it's GPS position to the website so 

Sources available at <a href="http://github.com/LeipeLeon/optocht/">http://github.com/LeipeLeon/optocht/</a>